{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was freezing and waiting for 4 o' clock in the morning to get up to get that-- the bus that took me a little bit farther.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there I took my bike.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I knocked at the farmer's house, I-- they spoke-- they didn't speak French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They spoke a patois.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was very-- you couldn't understand it even if you knew French.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a language I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you wanted to barter for a few potatoes, some flour, perhaps a bit of butter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And soap sometimes-- you know, soap was very scarce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had to beg them to let you have with, with-- for your nails, or screws, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had already several kilos of nails on you-- with you, you know, which was difficult on your bike, too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were not the modern bikes of today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to use your legs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to manage to get lentils and potatoes and flour and, and-- enough, you know, to fill up my, my rucksack and my, my case.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I came down the mountains and came into La Puy, I had to face the German Army there and the French police.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you were not allowed to go out of the country and get food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to hide my bicycle behind the bench.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to hide the food behind another bench.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my heart just dropped into my shoes, you know, because I was trembling away-- I wasn't only 17-- and wait for the train to arrive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the train arrived, you know, I quickly took all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to manage the bicycle, the food, and everything to get into the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
